  _lines:
  - I won't intude for too long then.
  - You probably have more poeple to cater to.
  - This place tends to attract quite a crowd.
  - I commend you.
  - If I were in your position, I would tire of it easily.
  - Regardless, I merely request a drink to satiate my thirst.
